            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic quiescit in pace <lb n="2"/>Ursicina qui vixit <lb n="3"/>annos V et mensis <note>sic</note> <lb n="4"/>XI et dies III Elpidius <lb n="5"/>et Ursula filiae primae na<lb break="no" n="6"/>t<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> posuerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Unterhalb der Inschrift Darstellung eines Olivenbaums mit symmetrisch flankierenden Tauben.</p>
            </div>
